|------|--------|
| `tests/test_game.py` | **Created** — 17 new tests for all 7 acceptance criteria |
| `src/monopoly/game.py` | Fixed `_build_result` to return richest player when max_turns reached |
| `tests/test_game_invariants.py` | Updated invariant test to match new max_turns spec |

**Result:** 462/462 tests passing (zero regressions).
