**Issue #20: Bankruptcy Detection and Forced Liquidation** — fully implemented via TDD.

### What was built

**`src/monopoly/bankruptcy.py`** — refactored and extended:

| Function | Status |
|----------|--------|
| `attempt_payment(player, amount, creditor, game_state, strategy) -> bool` | ✅ Fixed liquidation order (houses first, then mortgage) |
