   - All 10 `CardEffect` variants handled; `ValueError` raised for unknown effects

2. **`tests/test_card_effects.py`** — 48 tests written before implementation (TDD):
   - One test class per effect type
   - All required edge cases: `move_relative` wrapping past Go without salary, 0 active opponents, 0 buildings, `move_to_nearest` board wrap

**Key design decisions:**
- `CardResult` is minimal (movement + landing modifier only) — cash mutations happen as side effects (SRP)
- `LandingModifier` is `None` when no rent hint params are present (YAGNI)
- `go_to_jail` fully mutates player state directly (position, in_jail, consecutive_doubles) as specified
- Coexists cleanly with existing `effects.py` (used by `turn.py`) — no regressions

**Result:** 48/48 new tests pass, 620/620 full suite passes.
